(1, 'UG', 1, 'all-india-medical', 'All India Medical Admission Process', './assets/images/AIMAP.jpeg', 'All India Medical Admission Process', '<p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Medical Counselling Committee of DGHS in Ministry of Health and Family Welfare, Govt. of India, New Delhi is conducting Online Counselling for allotment of Under Graduate (MBBS/BDS) seats to the eligible and qualified candidates under 15% All India Quota in participating Government Medical/Dental Colleges of the country every year.<br><br>The allotment of seat to the candidates is made based on the NEET-UG Examination conducted by National Testing Agency (NTA). also conducting Online Counselling for allotment of Under Graduate (MBBS/BDS) seats to the eligible and qualified candidates in participating Deemed Universities of the country on the basis of NEET (UG) examination conducted by NTA. Qualified and eligible candidates are required to register on the MCC website i.e. www.mcc.nic.in to participate in the counselling process for allotment of seat. MCC does not allot any seat either on nomination basis or manually.</p>', '<div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8\">\n    <!-- AIQ Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for AIQ</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The Candidate should have qualified NEET UG</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Domicile free</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">As per norms of NMC</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Deemed University Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for Deemed University</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The Candidate should have qualified NEET UG</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Domicile free</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AIIMS Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for AIIMS</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The Candidate should have qualified NEET UG</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Domicile free</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Eligibility conditions as per AIIMS will be applicable</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- ESIC Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for Insured Person Quota candidates of ESIC</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Candidate should have Ward of Insured Persons certificate with distinct number</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Candidate should have qualified All India Examination i.e. NEET UG for the relevant year</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Domicile free</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Reservation for the MBBS/BDS seats under Insured Persons\' Quota would be as per extant Govt. of India guidelines</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- DU Internal Quota Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for DU Internal Quota</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The eligibility conditions have been provided by DU Authority for State Quota admission to MBBS/BDS course</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- VMMC & SJH Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility condition for VMMC & SJH; ABVIMS & RML; ESIC, Dental State Quota seats as provided by the I.P. University authorities</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The location of the school/college from which the Candidates have passed the qualifying examination will form the criteria for deciding the region of the candidates. The candidates who have studied 10+2 (11th and 12th) classes in the recognized schools/colleges in Delhi and passed the qualifying examination from any school/college</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- AMU Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for Internal Quota Seats of AMU</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The Eligibility conditions for AMU Internal candidates given by AMU Authorities</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Candidates are advised to check the eligibility criteria for internal quota of AMU on the website of AMU</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">MCC has no role to play in deciding the internal eligibility criteria for AMU</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- BHU Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for Banaras Hindu University</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Domicile free</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Candidates who have qualified the NEET are eligible to apply for the same</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- JIPMER Eligibility -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0\">\n        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold\">Eligibility Condition for JIPMER Internal seats</p>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The Candidate should have qualified NEET UG</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">Candidates are advised to go through Annexure-10 for the eligibility quota details. The same has been provided by JIPMER Authorities, MCC has no role in the same</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <span class=\"mr-2 text-black font-bold mt-0.5\">•</span>\n                <span class=\"text-sm sm:text-base\">The list of domicile candidates for internal seats is provided by State authorities of Puducherry. Medical counselling committee has no role to play in determination of domicile status of the candidate. In case of any discrepancy, the candidates are advised to approach State Authorities</span>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"mt-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4 text-lg sm:text-xl\">Quota Distribution</h3>\n        <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                    <table class=\"w-full table-fixed border-collapse\">\n                      <tbody class=\"bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200\">\n                             <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase\">Colleges</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase text-right\">Quota</td>\n                            </tr>\n                       \n                            <!-- Row 1 -->\n                            <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                               <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">All India Government Colleges (MBBS/BDS)</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">15%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 2 -->\n                             <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Banaras Hindu University (MBBS/BDS)</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 3 -->\n                             <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">AIIMS (MBBS)</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 4 -->\n                             <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Banaras Hindu University (BHU)</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 5 -->\n                           <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                               <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">JIPMER</td>\n                               <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 6 -->\n                            <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Aligarh Muslim University</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 7 -->\n                             <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Jamia (BDS)</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 8 -->\n                            <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                               <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">ESIC</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">15%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <!-- Row 9 -->\n                             <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Deemed University</td>\n                                <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">100%</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n', '<div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n  <table class=\"w-full table-fixed border-collapse\">\n    <tbody class=\"bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200\">\n      <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50\">\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase\">Category</td>\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase text-right\">Reservation Percentage</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Scheduled Caste (SC)</td>\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">15%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Scheduled Tribes (ST)</td>\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">7.5%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Other Backward Classes (NCL)</td>\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">27%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">EWS</td>\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">10%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\">\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">Person with Disability (PwD)</td>\n        <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 text-right\">5%</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n<p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mt-4\">No any Category Reservation for Deemed Universities.</p>\n</div>\n', '<div id=\"fees\" class=\"bg-white rounded-lg mb-8 overflow-hidden scroll-mt-30\">\n    <div class=\"p-4 md:p-6\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4\">For Normal University</h2>\n     