(6, 'UG', 1, 'Maharashtra Ayush Admission Process', 'Maharashtra Ayush Admission Process', './assets/images/MHTCET.jpeg', 'Maharashtra Ayush Admission Process', 'BPT admission is offered through NEET UG in some states.', '10+2 with PCB and NEET qualification.', 'Reservation as per state policy.', 'Govt: ₹10,000 – ₹50,000 | Private: ₹1–3 Lakhs', 'Entrance → Counselling → Admission', '\r\n    <div>\r\n        <h3><strong>Q1. What is BPT?</strong></h3>\r\n        <p>Bachelor of Physiotherapy.</p>\r\n\r\n        <h3><strong>Q2. Is NEET mandatory for BPT?</strong></h3>\r\n        <p>Depends on state and college.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    ', 6, 1, '2026-01-05 10:45:40', '2026-01-05 11:03:38'),
